{"tw": {"2421350": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "雙修武林", "steam_appid": 2421350, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《雙修武林》是一款武侠题材的角色扮演游戏，在游戏中，玩家将扮演一个初出茅庐的江湖小生，在战斗和历练中结识红颜知己，并与她们共同闯荡这个充满危机与机遇的江湖世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抛枕翠云光，绣衣闻异香。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜来珠锁动，惊觉银屏梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脸慢笑盈盈，相看无限情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【主角簡介】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/890323b595801c28e890a2b5eff8bfbf.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飛鴻斷霞，蕭衡雁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >26歲，孤女，英氣非凡，現任西子亭掌院。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/900b953786463633982db1347d3eab05.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尹念念</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28歲，親王妾，身材嬌小，曾被男主父親救過，對男主之父心生情愫，後將這份愛移情於男主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/adcc5b56c4996f6d56c4171a27d6acaf.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雲行鶴影 暮寒雪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24歲，雪山派。兩年前受情人蠱惑，奪取秘籍，殺師並叛出師門，一直遭到門派追殺，後得男主相救，因中屍毒，委身男主，後欲提升修為，與男主「雙修」，是男主上乘武學的啟蒙老師。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/5a0a415b8c1ddf6da3eb7aaee48d0b7f.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虞紫瑤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20歲，魯東堂，一年前因吳月先謀奪控制魯東堂丈夫慘死，又被吳月先蹂躪玩弄。表面上是吳月先收服的女人，實際上卻忍辱負重隱在吳月先身邊伺機報仇，後因對吳月先動手復仇失敗命懸一線，被男主以同類型雙修功法所救。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/f521f2f584269eb1b8e211425cb643a6.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑迦麗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18歲，獻王教教主，戴著恐怖面具統御眾人，無人知其女兒身的秘密，後被男主撞破女子身份並發生親密關係。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【戰鬥簡介】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*多種戰鬥流派任你選擇，上百種技能自由搭配組合，絕世武功助您馳騁江湖；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*戰鬥內隨機產生道具、敵人以及升級獎勵，每一局都是全新體驗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*地圖中還有寶箱，開啟寶箱可以獲得技能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【遊戲特色】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過10W字新武俠風格劇情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過100張劇情CG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過300條女角色中文配音</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《雙修武林》是一款武侠题材的角色扮演游戏，在游戏中，玩家将扮演一个初出茅庐的江湖小生，在战斗和历练中结识红颜知己，并与她们共同闯荡这个充满危机与机遇的江湖世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抛枕翠云光，绣衣闻异香。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜来珠锁动，惊觉银屏梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脸慢笑盈盈，相看无限情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【主角簡介】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/890323b595801c28e890a2b5eff8bfbf.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飛鴻斷霞，蕭衡雁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >26歲，孤女，英氣非凡，現任西子亭掌院。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/900b953786463633982db1347d3eab05.avif?t=1756566164\" width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尹念念</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28歲，親王妾，身材嬌小，曾被男主父親救過，對男主之父心生情愫，後將這份愛移情於男主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421350/extras/adcc